2
00:00:09,169 --> 00:00:11,848
The relief aid money of (Nrs.) 22,000
[approximately USD 200]

3
00:00:11,848 --> 00:00:13,088
has been already spent.

4
00:00:13,088 --> 00:00:17,054
Nowadays, we are somehow surviving.

5
00:00:17,054 --> 00:00:20,214
We are in a hard
